# ==== Commit Messages =============================================================

# ==== Commit Message (Commit Summary) Format ======================================
# <emoji> <commit-type >: #<IssueNumber> <subject>
# 
# <description>

# ==== Example =====================================================================
# ✨ feat: Create shared display components for the top page and service page
# ✏️ fix: #123 Corrected a typo in the Terms of Use

# ==== commit-type ( Prefix ) ======================================================
# fix: ------------------ Bug fix
# hotfix: --------------- Emergency bug fix
# feat: ----------------- New feature (short for feature)
# docs: ----------------- Documentation-only changes
# style: ---------------- Code formatting changes like whitespace, line breaks, etc.
# refactor:	------------- Code restructuring (e.g., refactoring)
# test: ----------------- Adding or correcting tests
# chore: ---------------- Changes related to build tools or auto-generated files/libraries

# ==== Emojis ======================================================================
# 🐛 :bug: --------------- Bug fix (fix)
# 🩹 :adhesive_bandage: -- Fix Lint errors or code style (style)
# 🚧 :construction: ------ Work In Progress (WIP)
# ✨ :sparkles: ---------- New feature (feat)
# 🎉 :tada: -------------- Major feature release worth celebrating (feat)
# 🚀 :rocket: ------------ Performance improvements (feat)
# 🎨 :art: --------------- Visual changes like CSS styling (feat)
# 💄 :lipstick: ---------- UI improvements (feat)
# 🔒️ :lock: -------------- Fix typos (docs)
# ✏️ :pencil: ------------ Security improvements (feat)
# 📝 :memo: -------------- Documentation updates (docs)
# ♻️ :recycle: ----------- Code refactoring (refactor)
# 🗑️ :wastebasket: ------- Remove code or files (refactor)
# 💚 :green_heart: ------- Fix CI builds or test improvements (test)
# ⬆️ :arrow_up: ---------- Dependency updates (chore)
# 🔖 :bookmark: ---------- Release / Version tags.

# ==== Appendix ====================================================================
# https://gist.github.com/joshbuchea/6f47e86d2510bce28f8e7f42ae84c716
# https://gitmoji.dev/
